
Business Problem

The business observed strong sales but inconsistent profitability. The goal was to identify why profits were declining and which segments were responsible.

Approach

Data checks and validation in SQL

KPI analysis (sales, profit, margin, discount)

Loss driver analysis by category/subcategory/region

Customer-level profitability analysis

Power BI dashboard to communicate insights interactively

Outcome

The dashboard enables stakeholders to quickly pinpoint loss sources and take corrective action on discounts and product strategy.


